Corporate report

Apprenticeships (in England): vision for 2020

From:
Department for Business, Innovation & Skills
First published:
7 December 2015
Part of:
Further education and training

Plan for how we will increase the quality and quantity of apprenticeships, achieving 3 million apprenticeships by 2020.

Ref: BIS/15/651 PDF, 1.53MB, 13 pages

Detail

This publication outlines the government’s plan for:

  • increasing the quality and quantity of apprenticeships
  • achieving 3 million apprenticeships by 2020

This publication sets out what is expected of all main stakeholders, employers, education and training providers and government working together.
